4
00:00:15,406 --> 00:00:20,061
People in the past have suggested that I enter photo contests.

5
00:00:20,062 --> 00:00:25,129
Photography is how I escape reality. There's nothing I really want to convey.

6
00:00:25,129 --> 00:00:27,113
I don't need to show anyone.

7
00:00:27,114 --> 00:00:30,177
I'd be embarrassed to show anyone.

8
00:00:30,177 --> 00:00:31,898
That's what this was to me.

9
00:00:31,898 --> 00:00:36,640
♫ I'm waiting for one word ♫

10
00:00:36,640 --> 00:00:40,060
♫ It looks like I saw love ♫

11
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:44,150
Take photos of me.

12
00:00:44,150 --> 00:00:48,372
In the same industry.

13
00:00:48,372 --> 00:00:50,971
What a benevolent king.

14
00:00:50,971 --> 00:00:53,417
My beautiful monarch.

15
00:00:54,920 --> 00:01:00,009
You've bestowed this lowly servant of such warmth.

16
00:01:00,009 --> 00:01:03,053
If I can be by your side,

17
00:01:03,053 --> 00:01:08,340
I would take on this reckless challenge time and time again.

18
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:12,810
♫ Is it close to you? ♫

19
00:01:12,810 --> 00:01:17,000
♫ Let me drown in the depths of my chest ♫

20
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,613
So creepy.

21
00:01:36,980 --> 00:01:39,690
[My Beautiful Man Season 2 | Eternal]

22
00:01:39,690 --> 00:01:45,380
♫ I couldn't love anyone other than you,
I just can't imagine this scenery ♫

23
00:01:45,380 --> 00:01:51,030
♫ You are as unreachable as the moon,
this has always made me sad ♫

24
00:01:51,030 --> 00:01:53,560
♫ Even if you complain I'm persistent, ♫

25
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:56,740
♫ There are things I cannot give up ♫

26
00:01:56,740 --> 00:01:59,130
♫ I'll tell you hundreds of millions of times, ♫

27
00:01:59,130 --> 00:02:02,320
♫ "My great and beautiful man" ♫

28
00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:04,810
♫ If you push back, ♫

29
00:02:04,810 --> 00:02:07,960
♫ You will challenge all of the recklessness ♫

30
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:10,420
♫ It's the first time I feel this way ♫

31
00:02:10,420 --> 00:02:13,280
♫ God, tell me that ♫

32
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:15,650
♫ This happiness is eternal ♫

33
00:02:15,650 --> 00:02:17,957
[My Beautiful Man | Episode 3]

34
00:02:18,877 --> 00:02:21,610
So what are you sending?

35
00:02:21,610 --> 00:02:25,281
Oh, I'm still not sure.

36
00:02:26,381 --> 00:02:28,420
What about one of Kiyoi?

37
00:02:28,970 --> 00:02:31,858
Well, but Kiyoi is a celebrity.

38
00:02:31,858 --> 00:02:33,982
Oh, right.

39
00:02:33,982 --> 00:02:36,265
It'd be bad if people found out.

40
00:02:36,266 --> 00:02:37,812
Yes.

41
00:02:37,812 --> 00:02:40,288
But what a shame.

42
00:02:40,288 --> 00:02:45,322
His portraits have a different vibe about them.

43
00:02:45,322 --> 00:02:47,104
There is love.

44
00:02:48,547 --> 00:02:51,712
A world with only the two of you.

45
00:02:52,506 --> 00:02:54,704
Our own world?

46
00:02:58,771 --> 00:03:01,069
That's just ridiculous.

47
00:03:01,069 --> 00:03:03,957
I'm clearly not worthy of being at Kiyoi's side.

48
00:03:03,957 --> 00:03:07,584
Even if I happened to become a photographer,

49
00:03:07,585 --> 00:03:10,335
I would never expect to be on his level.

50
00:03:10,336 --> 00:03:13,125
But even so,

51
00:03:13,125 --> 00:03:17,616
I'd be happy with him just noticing me as the pebble over there.

52
00:03:17,617 --> 00:03:20,074
She's so pretty.

53
00:03:21,804 --> 00:03:23,610
Anna.

54
00:03:26,148 --> 00:03:28,691
I mean her character.

55
00:03:31,547 --> 00:03:36,356
It's such an extreme stage play, but she still seems so pure.

56
00:03:36,356 --> 00:03:39,093
Is purity born from ignorance?

57
00:03:40,700 --> 00:03:45,430
You don't know anything, so you can't realize your sins.

58
00:03:45,933 --> 00:03:48,951
She doesn't know, so she doesn't realize.

59
00:03:48,951 --> 00:03:52,898
This kind of play is so amazing.

60
00:03:58,859 --> 00:04:00,490
Hey.

61
00:04:01,723 --> 00:04:03,311
Oh, sorry.

62
00:04:03,311 --> 00:04:05,728
You were just so beautiful.

63
00:04:07,445 --> 00:04:10,522
Any facial expression looks good on you,

64
00:04:10,523 --> 00:04:14,884
